*(''cat''): [[kitty]], [[kitty-cat]], [[puss]], [[pussy-cat]]
*(''female genitalia''): (''all taboo slang'') [[beaver]], [[box]], [[cunny]], [[cunt]], [[fanny]] (''UK''), [[gash]], [[hole]], [[minge]], [[quim]], [[slit]], [[snatch]], [[twat]] (''see also'' [[WikiSaurus:vagina]] ''and'' [[WikiSaurus:female genitalia]])
